Demonstrators in Ukraine attacked buses carrying Ukrainians and displaced foreigners from Wuhan to Novi Sanzhary.
Students from northeastern India, bordering with China, and students in large cities in India supposedly suffered persecution related to the outbreak of coronavirus.
